    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-04-11T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-04-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="394"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d394">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 818.00/194</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Tinoco</persName> to President
                            <persName type="to">Wilson</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Translation]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">San José</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-04-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 11, 1917</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I hasten to bring to the knowledge of Your Excellency that to-day I have taken
                    possession in the presence of the National Assembly constituent, of the office
                    of President of the Republic to which I have been called by the free and
                    manifest will of my fellow citizens and it is my most fervent desire to sustain
                    with the Government which Your Excellency so fitly directs the most cordial and
                    sincere relations, and I make an expression of my own sentiments in asking Your
                    Excellency to be pleased to receive for the American Government and people, in
                    the present situation of war in which they are found, a message of devoted and
                    sincere sympathy.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">F. Tinoco</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
